  caller_name: Dave
  caller_dialogue: Hey, so just a week ago my neighbor was all fine and dandy, but
    recently he just won't stop hoarding bugs in his house. It would be fine if those
    creeps didn't crawl over to our place and give my kids lives like hell. He used
    to be so talkative, but now all he does is stare with those creepy eyes. I tried
    making a joke with him and he just stared at me.
